  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4906501">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4906501/" class="title-link">哲学是个什么玩意</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4906501"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/hk_carrot/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u34787543-16.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/hk_carrot/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Mr.Beginner</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-04-14"
      class="main-meta">2011-04-14 08:57:45</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4906501_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  谈哲学，我想先谈一下中国教育。在近代的中国教育体系里，重理轻文显而易见，包括现在也是，理工科的数量远大于文科生数量。其实这也是苏联模式的一个缩影，一个萝卜一个坑式的人才培养。姑且不论这种人为的人才培养模式的利与弊，起码回顾自己接受的教育历程，缺少哲学这门课...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4906501/#comments">(5回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">25有用 / 10没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4906501_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4906501_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1245774">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1245774/" class="title-link">流畅的哲学</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1245774"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1309461/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1309461-24.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1309461/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">瓜王</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-11-23"
      class="main-meta">2007-11-23 21:46:26</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1245774_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  个人认为，只有极高水平的人才能写出这样貌似“通俗易懂”的书。因为，只有把西方生硬的概念内化为自己的思想，转化为中国人的表达习惯，才能这样流淌地写出来。对比国内研究哲学的同仁们，写着别人弄不懂自己恐怕也弄不懂的欧化文章，陈嘉映的工作实在值得赞扬。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1245774/#comments">(5回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">11有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1245774_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1245774_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
